quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,"Izo ntumwa\tmugihe\tzashika\tku\tbantu b’intumwa\ty’Imana\tLutwi\t(iii) bafise ishusho ry’abantu"
  15,62,"Lutwi (iii) yavuze ati:- mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mu bantu mutazwi kandi nanje sindabazi"
  15,63,"Baca bishura bati:- twebwe tukuzaniye bimwe muvyo bahora bagirira ko amakenga"
  15,64,"Dushitse iwawe n’ukuri, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi muba vugisha ukuri"
  15,65,"Rero nugende n’abantu bawe mugice c’ijoro nawe ubakurikire inyuma yanyu ntihagire umwe muri mwebwe ahindukira inyuma, hanyuma mugende mutumbera iyo mwategetswe kuja"
  15,66,Hanyuma tumucira intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) kuri rya jambo yuko imizi yabo izocibwa mugitondo
  15,67,Haca haza abantu bo mugisagara banezerewe
  15,68,"Intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) yavuze iti:- mu vy’ukuri aba n’abashitsi banje ntimuntetereze"
  15,69,Kandi mutinye Imana yanyu ntimunkengere
  15,70,"Bavuga bati:- mbega twebwe ntitwakubujije kwakira abantu"
  15,71,"Yavuze ati:- aba bose n’abigeme banje nimwaba mwebwe muri mubagira ibikorwa"
  15,72,Ndarahiye k’ubuzima bwawe mu vy’ukuri abo bantu bari mububorerwe bwabo bataya taya hirya no hino
  15,73,Mumwanya ibihano biraba fata mugihe izuba ryaseruka
  15,74,"Hanyuma\tduca\ttugira\tivyo\tbisagara\tkuba\thasi\thejuru,\thanyuma tubashungurira imvura y’isegenya irimwo ivyondo vyo mumuriro udahera"
  15,75,"Mu vy’ukuri\tmuri ibi\tvyose harimwo icirwa ku bantu bapima\tibintu n’ibindi"
  15,76,N’ibi bisagara twahoneje biri munzira bacamwo mumwanya wose
  15,77,Ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo icirwa kubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  15,78,Mu vy’ukuri abantu bo mumashamba bari mubahemukiye imitima yabo
  15,79,"Kuri\tivyo\ttwarabahanye,\tn’ibi\tbisagara\tuko\tari\tbibiri\tvyari\tmunzira ziboneka neza"